title: Northhaven Ad
author: Farrent_
pages:
#- §4Make Northhaven Home§0
§0In the northern regions of the Aquilan§0
§0state of Garzweiler lies the construction site of a new luxury city. The aim of this city is to entertain the more experienced players & to provide excellent facilities for them to use.
#- The city is starting to take shape, & there is now a direct line to it from Aquila (Local Lines). Feel free to visit at any time! If you like what you see, and want to live there, you can get a prebuilt house or buy a plot.§0
§0
§0~ Farrent
